{"tid":110764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁特插曾俊華6成人住公營房屋目標推高價樓","createTime":"2017-02-07T02:39:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-07T03:44:16.000Z","uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"abe4da5390bb5197fbc861bf6cade5fb37dfcf79","tid":110764,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T02:39:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170207/56271622\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170207%2F56271622&d=hmtFoPnP%2FIv5fOqUL3ZUajPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=64842da2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170207%2F56271622&h=db288ebc\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170207/56271622</a><br />\n<br />\n 特首參選人曾俊華的政綱提出6成港人住公營房屋目標，特首梁振英今早出席行會前見記者，直指有關目標是一個重大的策略轉變，若要達成，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">政府就算不再向市場賣地，也未必可提供供應，並會將本港過去長時期以來的土地開發計劃都用作發展公營房屋，而市場沒有私人住宅供應，樓價會提高，逼使很多本身有能力購買私樓的人輪候公營房屋。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n梁振英指現屆政府提出的概念，是10年建屋目標中的46萬個新單位，當中6成是公營房屋，4成屬私人住宅，概念清楚及科學化，認為曾俊華應向社會交代清楚。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不如試下10年唔賣地轉哂起公屋睇下樓價會跌到谷底定升上外太空 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"211a9034c6fa4a9756a6636c6e3189b3e466e341","tid":110764,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T02:42:01.000Z","msg":"十成公屋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f39a7c3db2a9eb481e520cad2ea07955ffd24565","tid":110764,"uid":11417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T02:42:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"178efe344c62d562877eb9ab9b8a476e5b494937","tid":110764,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T02:43:19.000Z","msg":"而家市場需要政府資助屋 <br />\